# Package management conventions

## Python (uv)

- Use `uv` to manage Python dependencies (source of truth: `pyproject.toml` + `uv.lock`).
- Install/sync dependencies with `uv sync`.
- Add Python deps with `uv add <pkg>` (or `uv add --dev <pkg>`).
- Run Python commands via `uv run ...` when appropriate.

## Node (China npm mirror)

- When installing Node deps in this repo, use a China-friendly registry mirror to avoid timeouts.
- Prefer project-local config so installs are reproducible:
  - add/keep `.npmrc` with `registry=https://registry.npmmirror.com`
  - avoid relying on global `npm config` on developer machines

